name: The Five Door Hillgate Sideboard
description: The Five Door Hillgate is an Art Deco-inspired side cabinet with lustrous finishing. It will inject glamour and style into any room. The chamfered edge gives this cabinet intrigue and character, with five doors opening to reveal a satin interior with two adjustable shelves within, and additional customisation options for further storage if required. It is smartly elevated off the ground by three plinths exuding Art Deco influence.
